1
00:00:01,960 --> 00:00:06,000
National Radio and Television Administration.

2
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:47,720
Wan Xinxin, I'm really sorry.

3
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,680
Why should I?

4
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,639
No, come back.

5
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,320
No, on what grounds?

6
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:39,760
If everything is destiny.

7
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:43,800
Time to sleep.

8
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,440
Go to sleep.

9
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,440
You're really willing to spend big money

10
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,079
chasing after your true love.

11
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,940
Have you found your true love yet?

12
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,600
It's not that easy.

13
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,840
This time I'm deeply in love.

14
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,060
So I must search carefully

15
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,720
and definitely find her.

16
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:08,090
Your camera is pretty nice.

17
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,360
Don't break it. This lens is the most expensive part.

18
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,420
Who's breaking it?

19
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,770
Let me see how good this lens really is.

20
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,800
Xu Ke.

21
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:22,520
There's a handsome guy living across from your place,

22
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,400
and he's a foreigner too.

23
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,720
This is a camera.

24
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,520
What?

25
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,400
You're actually peeping on people?

26
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,880
I'm telling you, if someone catches us,

27
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,280
we'll both end up in jail.

28
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:30,560
So be it.

29
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,240
I'm not afraid.

30
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,200
I have nothing left anyway.

31
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:39,640
No job, can't go back home.

32
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,880
At least in jail I'd get food,

33
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:43,320
and I wouldn't have to worry about someone taking my son.

34
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:45,040
You've been watching too many Korean dramas.

35
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:47,320
Acting like the whole world is trying to steal your son.

36
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,240
What do you know? I saw it with my own eyes.

37
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,520
Qin Gang was holding my baby.

38
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,450
And Hua was holding a stack of cash.

39
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,840
If you ask me,

40
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,800
this Hua Ming isn't like what you described.

41
00:03:59,040 --> 00:03:59,720
I mean, apart from having

42
00:03:59,720 --> 00:04:01,360
a rather expressionless face,

43
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:03,360
I think he's a pretty decent person.

44
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,460
With how you've been tormenting him,

45
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:08,000
if he wanted to ruin you,

46
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,560
he could have done it in a minute.

47
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,560
Besides, from what you just told me,

48
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,440
I think in this case,

49
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:16,959
it was your sister who handed

50
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,959
the baby to Hua Ming herself.

51
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:21,740
So there's basically no chance he planned this.

52
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,360
Are you really the child's godfather or not?

53
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,240
I'm just analyzing the situation for you.

54
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,000
I don't care.

55
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:27,960
Nobody can mess with my baby boy.

56
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:28,840
Okay, okay.

57
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,640
Fine.

58
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:33,400
Xu Ke.

59
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,960
Why don't I just move in here

60
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,080
and you can move back home?

61
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,600
I'll help you keep an eye out for your true love.

62
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,460
How about that?

63
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:41,440
Come on, this is about love.

64
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,320
What are you thinking?

65
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,560
It's not something someone else can do for me.

66
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:46,760
Besides, do you even know her? Do you know who to watch for?

67
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,720
I don't even want to stay at your place anyway.

68
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:51,520
Don't look a gift horse in the mouth.

69
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:52,600
Easy for you to say.

70
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,040
We're two mouths to feed, one big and one small.

71
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,240
Both of us need to eat.

72
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,480
The most basic needs

73
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,720
can still be taken care of.

74
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,760
But what if someday

75
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,240
you actually win over that true love of yours?

76
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,040
And the girl insists on committing to you?

77
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,480
Then how will you introduce me and my son?

78
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,480
Here's my ex-wife and son?

79
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,640
Is that appropriate?

80
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:08,240
Ex-wife?

81
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:10,000
I can't be a burden to you.

82
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:12,360
What should we do then?

83
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,360
What about me?

84
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,440
Ever since I met

85
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,040
those jinxes Qin Gang and Liu Wei,

86
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,280
my luck has been terrible.

87
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,280
I've lost everything.

88
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,400
No job, can't go home.

89
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,360
They're pushing me to the edge.

90
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,080
Right?

91
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:25,280
Wait, your hair.

92
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,480
I got it!

93
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,140
Tell me.

94
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,420
Actually, you just

95
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,200
messed up a business deal.

96
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,400
It's not the end of the world, right?

97
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:36,400
What do you mean it's not a big deal?

98
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,680
You don't know our female boss.

99
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,280
That company is her life.

100
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,280
I've basically destroyed her life.

101
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:44,140
She'll strangle me if she sees me.

102
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,600
So Lady Company collapsed overnight,

103
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,880
all because of you, Wan Xinxin.

104
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:50,210
You're something else.

105
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,960
You've really done it this time.

106
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,320
Stop talking.

107
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:53,720
Fine.

108
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,080
I feel like I'm going crazy.

109
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,800
I really want to make it up to the boss,

110
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,800
but I don't have the ability.

111
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,520
I'm almost homeless.

112
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,680
There is a solution.

113
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,660
It can both make up for the loss

114
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:08,120
and let you return to the company with your head held high.

115
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,280
Really?

116
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,140
Is it reliable?

117
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,440
Absolutely.

118
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:15,480
Look, we live in a resource integration society.

119
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,520
You just need to find one client,

120
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:20,210
close the deal and bring them to your boss.

121
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,120
That's it.

122
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,840
That's it? You think clients are just waiting for me?

123
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,970
You think I can just grab one anywhere?

124
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,880
I've already thought of something for you.

125
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,940
I shot a catalog for a company before.

126
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:32,480
They mentioned wanting to expand.

127
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:34,300
They're doing quite well.

128
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,159
Wait, you?

129
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,440
What kind of good clients could you know?

130
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,320
Are you kidding me?

131
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,400
You think I only know how to date?

132
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:45,060
I'm also a man with career ambitions.

133
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,360
Alright, Xu Ke.

134
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,220
How about this?

135
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,240
You invite him over and I'll talk to him.

136
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,680
No, what are you thinking?

137
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,680
They're clients.

138
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,800
You think they come whenever you call like I do?

139
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,200
Go home, take a hot shower,

140
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,280
feed your pet,

141
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,600
get a good night's sleep.

142
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,800
Tomorrow, I promise,

143
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,680
you'll wake up to a brand new start.

144
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,260
I guess that's all I can do.

145
00:07:08,040 --> 00:07:09,880
I hope dreams come true.

146
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,200
God bless me.

147
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,480
You're back.

148
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,000
Why are you here?

149
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,120
I wanted to surprise you.

150
00:07:35,640 --> 00:07:37,880
I'm staying with you tonight.

151
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:38,920
Is that okay?

152
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,600
No. You need to move in now.

153
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,810
Isn't that a bit rushed?

154
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,840
Are you that afraid of your mother finding out about me?

155
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:53,240
No, I just think it's a bit

156
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,320
inappropriate right now.

157
00:07:55,320 --> 00:07:57,180
Then when will it be appropriate?

158
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,360
Weiwei, I know this

159
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,880
is unfair to you.

160
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,800
But you need to understand.

161
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,000
Everything I have comes from my mother.

162
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,920
I don't want to hurt her.

163
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,730
Alright, stop talking.

164
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,640
I know you're in a difficult position.

165
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,840
But you can't keep hiding this forever.

166
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:20,560
For now, I'll just hide it as long as I can.

167
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,820
Jiang Kaiyang.

168
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,120
You need to explain yourself today.

169
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:02,900
What are you doing? Why are you acting crazy?

170
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,600
Where were you today?

171
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,660
You didn't go to work. Where were you?

172
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,560
Xu Chunli, what are you doing?

173
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:10,200
Why did you come to my workplace?

174
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,280
You... this...

175
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,760
What? Am I not allowed to go there?

176
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:15,440
Are you afraid I'll discover your dirty little secret?

177
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,400
Let me tell you something.

178
00:09:16,400 --> 00:09:18,200
I saw you today with that vixen.

179
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,120
Fooling around together.

180
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,520
Don't try to deny it today.

181
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:22,380
Xu Chunli, you've lost your mind.

182
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,960
Let me tell you.

183
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,520
If something really happens to me,

184
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:27,520
it will be all your fault.

185
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,360
Got it?

186
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,050
What's going on?

187
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:30,880
Explain yourself to me!

188
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,210
How dare you grab my bag!

189
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,240
Give it to me!

190
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,300
What are you doing?

191
00:09:34,560 --> 00:09:35,280
You're going through my bag?

192
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:37,410
How many things are you hiding from me?

193
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:40,680
What is this?

194
00:09:45,800 --> 00:09:47,160
Why do you have so much money?

195
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,620
Let me tell you, Xu Chunli.

196
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,920
I'll have more and more money in the future.

197
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,140
So you've backed down.

198
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,920
Old jerk.

199
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:31,000
Wait, what are you doing here?

200
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,840
I wrote that note.

201
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:35,960
I can read.

202
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,400
You call this an apology?

203
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:42,720
Isn't it?

204
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:43,820
How could it be?

205
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,640
It should count.

206
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,240
No.

207
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,080
Doesn't it count?

208
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,000
Fine.

209
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,120
See?

210
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,480
Whether it counts or not, Miss Wan,

211
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,920
I would like to formally

212
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,410
apologize to you again.

213
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:56,120
Miss Wan Xinxin,

214
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,400
I was wrong, I'm guilty, it was my fault.

215
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,400
I'm sorry.

216
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,920
Actually, I wasn't planning to blame you today.

217
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,200
But remember this:

218
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,560
never take Bao to see that Qin guy again.

219
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,800
Wait, Wan Xinxin.

220
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:13,160
Could you let Qin Gang see Bao?

221
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,640
Say that again.

222
00:11:15,920 --> 00:11:18,360
Don't get angry. Let me finish first.

223
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,400
No matter what happened

224
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:21,800
between you and Qin Gang,

225
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:24,200
the child is innocent, right?

226
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,930
You can't deny a child the right to see his father.

227
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,880
I was finally starting

228
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,520
to have some good feelings toward you,

229
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,920
and now they're all gone.

230
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,520
Don't worry about my business.

231
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:41,280
How about I write another one?

232
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:48,440
This definitely counts.

233
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,520
Do you understand?

234
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,000
You should have explained it clearly to me.

235
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,280
How was I supposed to know that woman

236
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:03,640
was some kind of financial advisor or whatever?

237
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,560
What am I going to do with you?

238
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,720
How am I supposed to explain everything to you?

239
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,200
Look at you, your mind is full of

240
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,480
those petty affairs between men and women.

241
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,960
What else do you think about?

242
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,280
I may not understand everything,

243
00:12:13,280 --> 00:12:14,480
but I know you.

244
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,640
Don't lie to me.

245
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,530
When have I ever lied to you?

246
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,640
You have nothing better to do all day.

247
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,720
You're so idle.

248
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,040
Why don't you take some time

249
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,720
to take care of our home?

250
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:27,400
Look at these past few days.

251
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:29,560
You're always running to your sister's place,

252
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,880
neglecting our home,

253
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,880
and now you're meddling in my business.

254
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,480
I'm telling you,

255
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:36,120
sooner or later you'll make yourself sick with all this idleness.

256
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:38,400
If I'm sick, it's because you drove me to it.

257
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,160
Jiang Kaiyang, let me tell you something.

258
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,200
You better be careful,

259
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:43,120
or I'll catch you red-handed one day.

260
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,080
Impossible.

261
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,240
Xu Chunli.

262
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:48,560
I'm not like your nouveau riche brother-in-law.

263
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,580
How could I do such things?

264
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,480
I, Jiang Kaiyang, am a dignified

265
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,720
deputy division-level government official.

266
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,720
I would never do anything so worthless.

267
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,600
Look at you,

268
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,040
Xu Chunli, you are

269
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:01,520
an official's wife, aren't you?

270
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:03,400
Yet you showed up at my workplace.

271
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:05,280
Do you know how bad that looks?

272
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,920
Do you realize what consequences this could have

273
00:13:07,920 --> 00:13:09,800
for my political career?

274
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:13,000
I didn't say anything at your workplace.

275
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:15,480
Then what else do you want?

276
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,920
Let me tell you, Xu Chunli.

277
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:19,120
I'm warning you,

278
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:21,320
stay out of my business from now on.

279
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,580
Take the money.

280
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:54,410
