00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,680
Hello.

565
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:51,120
You've already resigned and got out clean.

566
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:54,000
Now you're walking right back into the trap.

567
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,480
I didn't want to come back.

568
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,940
Mr. Shi asked me to return.

569
00:26:57,280 --> 00:26:59,520
You're just asking for trouble.

570
00:27:01,560 --> 00:27:02,440
He's asleep.

571
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,120
Let me tell you.

572
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,440
That female devil,

573
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:07,280
if she corners you,

574
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,560
remember

575
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:11,080
there's an escape route over there.

576
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,680
Just wait and see.

577
00:27:16,320 --> 00:27:18,050
Why are you all gathered there?

578
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:19,480
Don't you have work to do?

579
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,720
Buddha bless you.

580
00:27:21,560 --> 00:27:23,320
Wan Xinxin, come to my office.

581
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:36,320
Mr. Shi, I came today to apologize to you.

582
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:37,880
Apologize to me?

583
00:27:38,440 --> 00:27:41,500
Would you have come to apologize if I hadn't called you?

584
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:42,520
Wan Xinxin.

585
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:44,600
You really have no shame.

586
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,320
After making such a big mistake,

587
00:27:46,320 --> 00:27:48,050
don't you feel any guilt at all?

588
00:27:48,360 --> 00:27:49,600
Look at yourself.

589
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:52,400
You just hide when problems arise,

590
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:55,290
without any courage to take responsibility.

591
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:59,330
Think about it. Who deserves this behavior of yours?

592
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:01,160
I came back this time

593
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:03,940
because I really want to make up for my mistakes.

594
00:28:04,120 --> 00:28:06,120
Make up? How are you going to do that?

595
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:08,280
I haven't had a chance to tell you yet,

596
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:10,320
but I've been negotiating a project outside,

597
00:28:10,320 --> 00:28:12,360
and that client has a very clear intention

598
00:28:12,360 --> 00:28:13,400
to cooperate with us.

599
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,120
If we prepare a good proposal,

600
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:17,400
the client is very interested in working with us.

601
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:20,330
What about the client? Has the contract been signed?

602
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:23,040
Do you think I'm a three-year-old?

603
00:28:23,040 --> 00:28:25,200
You expect me to believe you just based on your word?

604
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,080
No, really.

605
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:28,340
I just need to prepare a proposal now.

606
00:28:28,800 --> 00:28:30,240
Once I finish that proposal,

607
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:32,300
I'll come back to discuss it with you.

608
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,600
Did I say you could leave?

609
00:28:36,560 --> 00:28:38,320
I know you can't bear to let me go.

610
00:28:38,320 --> 00:28:41,120
Don't worry, I definitely won't disappear again.

611
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,880
You can work here at the company.

612
00:28:42,880 --> 00:28:44,920
Stay at the company?

613
00:28:45,040 --> 00:28:46,080
Work here at the company,

614
00:28:46,080 --> 00:28:47,610
in your original position.

615
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:49,240
Okay.

616
00:29:04,320 --> 00:29:06,580
These are the materials Mr. Shi gave you.

617
00:29:09,040 --> 00:29:11,720
Just focus on writing a good proposal.

618
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,080
Alright.

619
00:29:34,160 --> 00:29:35,080
I'm sorry.

620
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,280
Mommy will be done soon.

621
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:30,120
Keep going.

622
00:30:42,200 --> 00:30:43,280
Don't cry.

623
00:30:45,080 --> 00:30:46,160
Don't cry.

624
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,580
What's going on? Why so noisy?

625
00:31:13,800 --> 00:31:17,400
Go back and take care of your child. Don't let it affect your work.

626
00:31:25,040 --> 00:31:27,520
Can you get your facts straight

627
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,980
before you start talking?

628
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:31,160
Yes, I admit

629
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:33,020
I was looking for Miss Shen today.

630
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,440
But do you know why

631
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,440
I was meeting her?

632
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:38,680
It was completely for our family's sake.

633
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,060
Do you understand?

634
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:44,000
Do you know what Miss Shen does?

635
00:31:44,720 --> 00:31:45,960
She's a financial advisor.

636
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:48,440
She has many investment channels.

637
00:31:48,480 --> 00:31:49,520
The money we made last time

638
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:50,980
was all thanks to her help.

639
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,720
Can't you see that?

640
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,280
Well,

641
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:56,400
who are you trying to fool?

642
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:58,200
If you've already made money,

643
00:31:58,240 --> 00:32:00,080
why do you still need to be with her?

644
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:01,280
Why the secret meetings?

645
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,680
You don't even have basic logic.

646
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:06,160
If I wanted to date her, would I be in that kind of place?

647
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:07,560
I'd just get a hotel room.

648
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,400
Who knows? Maybe you would.

649
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,400
Xu Chunli, let me tell you.

650
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:16,240
This Miss Shen has

651
00:32:16,240 --> 00:32:17,440
a 100-million-yuan project.

652
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,560
There's a lot of money to be made.

653
00:32:18,560 --> 00:32:20,320
Many people want to work with her,

654
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:21,320
but she ignores them completely.

655
00:32:21,320 --> 00:32:22,440
Why did she come to me?

656
00:32:22,440 --> 00:32:25,800
Because I approved some documents for her before.

657
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:26,680
Do you remember?

658
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:28,360
So I had to beg and plead

659
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:30,520
just to catch this last opportunity.

660
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:32,140
And now with your scene...

661
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,840
How much money could you make

662
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,490
that's got you so obsessed?

663
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,820
Not that much, just 1 or 2 million.

664
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:41,920
What? 1 or 2 million?

665
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,000
Now it's all gone. Down the drain.

666
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:48,080
Why didn't you explain this to me clearly?

667
00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,400
Being all secretive.

668
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:52,040
Would telling you have helped? Someone like you.

669
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:53,880
You follow me around all day.

670
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:56,120
Let me tell you, Xu Chunli.

671
00:32:56,120 --> 00:32:57,720
I had planned

672
00:32:57,800 --> 00:33:00,320
to earn this money and take you traveling abroad.

673
00:33:00,320 --> 00:33:01,560
And then for our daughter,

674
00:33:01,560 --> 00:33:03,560
to transfer her to a better school.

675
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:04,490
With your scene,

676
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:08,260
I've lost what would take several lifetimes of salary to earn.

677
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:09,880
Look at you.

678
00:33:10,280 --> 00:33:12,240
Look at yourself.

679
00:33:12,680 --> 00:33:15,840
If you had explained earlier, there wouldn't have been any problem.

680
00:33:15,840 --> 00:33:18,160
I'm not an unreasonable person.

681
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,200
Well,

682
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:22,280
why don't you call her again?

683
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,880
This is our situation.

684
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:36,920
Room and board included, with a 3-month probation period.

685
00:33:36,920 --> 00:33:38,680
During these three months, the monthly salary is

686
00:33:38,680 --> 00:33:39,640
2,500 yuan.

687
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:44,240
A 3-month probation period is quite long

688
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,600
for such little pay.

689
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:47,800
If you're willing to work, you can stay.

690
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,800
And if not, that's fine too.

691
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:54,120
Actually,

692
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,450
as long as you work hard,

693
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:59,360
a raise won't be a problem in the future.

694
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:03,400
2,500 yuan is too little, too little.

695
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:05,960
I don't hire male housekeepers.

696
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,880
I'm sorry, excuse me.

697
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,010
Please consider it.

698
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:11,900
What are you doing?

699
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:13,929
Miss Wan, what are you up to now?

700
00:34:14,239 --> 00:34:16,440
Can't you tell? I'm looking for a nanny.

701
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:18,840
No, you.

702
00:34:18,840 --> 00:34:20,199
Where are you looking for a nanny?

703
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:21,120
Online.

704
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,080
Finding a nanny online?

705
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:24,199
They don't even have professional training certificates.

706
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:25,600
How can that be reliable?

707
00:34:25,639 --> 00:34:27,040
Why wouldn't it be reliable?

708
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:27,800
It's perfectly fine.

709
00:34:27,800 --> 00:34:29,130
What's it to you anyway?

710
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,360
Excuse me, everyone.

711
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,639
Who are you calling unreliable?

712
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:33,440
Ladies, all of you.

713
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:34,280
Let me ask you something.

714
00:34:34,280 --> 00:34:37,199
Does anyone here have a health certificate or childcare qualification?

715
00:34:37,199 --> 00:34:38,760
Who has a qualification certificate

716
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:41,489
issued by a professional housekeeping company?

717
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:44,440
For 2,500, you still want someone certified?

718
00:34:44,440 --> 00:34:45,920
Then find one yourself.

719
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:48,000
Not reliable. Let's go.

720
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:48,800
Don't go!

721
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:49,280
I'm sorry.

722
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:50,159
Don't go! Wait.

723
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:53,159
Come back! Wait.

724
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:56,239
I'll raise it by another 1,000 for whoever agrees.

725
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,960
The baby is sleeping inside, right?

726
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:03,080
No. What did I do to you?

727
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:04,280
What's going on?

728
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,160
What grudge do you have against me?

729
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:06,360
Look, they all left.

730
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,800
I'm doing this for the baby's sake.

731
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,840
If she doesn't have a certificate...

732
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,900
No, I just don't have that much money.

733
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:16,120
Can you really pay 3,500?

734
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:17,640
Yes.

735
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,360
If you can pay 3,500,

736
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,200
I can do it.

737
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,480
What's your name?

738
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:26,320
My name is Xiaomei.

739
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,580
Do you have any experience in this field?

740
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,680
Well, I haven't taken care of others' children,

741
00:35:30,680 --> 00:35:32,210
but I have two kids of my own.

742
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:34,960
Then you must be quite experienced.

743
00:35:37,320 --> 00:35:38,520
Do you like children?

744
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:39,840
Of course I do.

745
00:35:40,280 --> 00:35:42,560
Good. You can start tomorrow.

746
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:12,160
Baby.

747
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:26,090
Oh my goodness! You scared me to death!

748
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:33,680
You're bathing the child with cold water and leaving the door open.

749
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:35,240
Don't you know children get sick easily?

750
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,120
It's none of your business.

751
00:36:36,120 --> 00:36:37,080
Get out now!

752
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,600
Come here, little one.

753
00:36:41,080 --> 00:36:41,520
Come.

754
00:36:41,520 --> 00:36:42,480
What are you doing?

755
00:36:42,480 --> 00:36:43,880
Okay, come here.

756
00:36:43,960 --> 00:36:46,120
Sister Wan said strangers shouldn't touch the child.

757
00:36:46,120 --> 00:36:47,280
Especially not you.

758
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,600
The child has a fever.

759
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:52,700
I'll take him to the hospital.

760
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:53,920
No way.

761
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:54,880
I used to be a doctor.

762
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:55,960
I think there's something wrong with the child.

763
00:36:55,960 --> 00:36:56,880
I need to take him to the hospital.

764
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:58,360
Will you take responsibility if something happens?

765
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,000
Let go.

766
00:37:01,600 --> 00:37:02,440
It's okay.

767
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:15,520
Wait.

768
00:37:29,320 --> 00:37:30,520
Hey, Xiaomei.

769
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,160
Hey, Xinxin.

770
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:34,080
That man took the child.

771
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,210
He took him away.

772
00:37:39,520 --> 00:37:41,440
Driver, turn around.

773
00:37:58,680 --> 00:37:59,120
Hey.

774
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,980
What have you done with my son?

775
00:38:01,200 --> 00:38:03,800
The child is sick. I brought him to see a doctor.

776
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:05,140
Come over here.

777
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,680
Changhai Hospital.

778
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:09,280
Okay, I'm coming right away.

779
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:12,290
Driver, take me to Changhai Hospital.

780
00:38:20,640 --> 00:38:21,440
Number 16.

781
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:21,970
Okay.

782
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:29,920
Driver, please hurry.

783
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:35,400
It's fine.

784
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,200
How is it, doctor?

785
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:40,840
Nothing serious.

786
00:38:41,240 --> 00:38:42,680
It's just a common flu.

787
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:44,680
Go get the medicine.

788
00:38:48,760 --> 00:38:50,320
This doesn't seem like a common flu.

789
00:38:50,320 --> 00:38:52,600
Look, he's been drowsy the whole time.

790
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:54,240
And look, he's in pain.

791
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:56,040
His eyes are clearly unfocused.

792
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,720
I suspect it's a sign of meningitis.

793
00:38:57,720 --> 00:38:59,520
Can we do a cerebrospinal fluid test?

794
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:00,280
We can do it.

795
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:02,800
But the child will suffer.

796
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,960
As long as it's for the child's safety and health,

797
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:07,090
we have to do it despite the suffering.

798
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,640
Xinxin.

799
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:11,240
What's wrong with the baby?

800
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:12,240
Mommy's here. Look at Mommy.

801
00:39:12,240 --> 00:39:12,920
Baby.

802
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:15,440
He was fine when I left this morning.

803
00:39:15,720 --> 00:39:16,320
Doctor?

804
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:18,120
It's not serious.

805
00:39:18,280 --> 00:39:20,280
Well, it's mainly just a common flu.

806
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:22,480
No, these are symptoms of meningitis.

807
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:23,200
Your diagnosis might be wrong.

808
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:24,200
Be quiet.

809
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,040
Okay.

810
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:26,680
Look, you two

811
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:29,280
should come back after you agree on something.

812
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:30,960
Next patient.

813
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:31,800
Thank you, doctor.

814
00:39:31,800 --> 00:39:33,080
Alright, thank you, doctor.

815
00:39:33,080 --> 00:39:33,540
Come on.

816
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:35,460
Wan Xinxin.

817
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:37,640
Didn't I tell you already?

818
00:39:37,640 --> 00:39:39,400
You can't find a nanny online.

819
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:41,000
The baby's immune system is weak right now.

820
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,760
You can't just let anyone watch him.

821
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,920
Don't talk about that now.

822
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,320
Why didn't you tell me

823
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,480
before taking him away today?

824
00:39:46,480 --> 00:39:48,080
Do you know how worried I was?

825
00:39:48,320 --> 00:39:49,880
Besides, the doctor already said

826
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,400
it's just a common flu.

827
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:53,520
You insisted on doing some kind of puncture.

828
00:39:53,520 --> 00:39:55,000
You're just a vet.

829
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,930
Why are you giving medical advice?

830
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,460
No puncture. No puncture.

831
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,520
Give me the baby first.

832
00:40:01,440 --> 00:40:02,170
Why should I?

833
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:05,160
Look, I left in a hurry.

834
00:40:05,160 --> 00:40:06,160
I didn't bring enough money.

835
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:08,160
You need to get medicine for the baby.

836
00:40:08,160 --> 00:40:09,290
Did you bring money?

837
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,560
I'm not unreliable like you.

838
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:13,040
Good.

839
00:40:13,040 --> 00:40:13,770
Take it easy.

840
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:15,320
Okay, come on.

841
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:17,960
Mommy will be right back.

842
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:18,320
Okay.

843
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:19,520
